song.title: Conga Track (1994)
song.info: SunSpire presents "Conga Track". An A500 4ch .mod written in OctaMED3 on 9th April 1994 and released in the Gravedigger Compo at Nordlicht Demoparty on 1st July 2016. Samples ripped with Action Replay MKIII from Turrican 1-3. Greetz to all visitors and Nordlicht Crew <3 Contact me at music@sunspire.audio
